text: Nabiyow ambiyak xaagu kol kak maaqqa haynem Yalli isi muxxoh kah yemqe mara ambiyak Nabii Aadam Samadaay Nabii Nuuc√ª luk nukkuqe marih Samadaay, Nabii Ibraahim Samadaay israa-iil (Nabii Yaq-qhuub kinnuk) Samadaay, kaadu keenik iimaanal tirri hayneeh farmoo kee nubuwwannuh doorre mari Racmaan kinni Rabbih aayootay kay inkittinaane tascasse keenil tan kirriyme waqdi weeqak kummaatak gomboh radan Yallak meesih
